{
 "file": "F_SCN/ERI_E02_AUD01_MES.BBQ",
 "count": 52,
 "lines": [
  {
   "i": 1,
   "en": "Ozaki"
  },
  {
   "i": 2,
   "en": "Eri, you here?! We did it, Eri!"
  },
  {
   "i": 3,
   "en": "Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 4,
   "en": "...What's going on?"
  },
  {
   "i": 5,
   "en": "Great news! We suddenly landed a"
  },
  {
   "i": 6,
   "en": "spot in the audition!"
  },
  {
   "i": 7,
   "en": "A special record-label recommendation"
  },
  {
   "i": 8,
   "en": "From the record label?"
  },
  {
   "i": 9,
   "en": "Yes. Your CD sales have been creeping"
  },
  {
   "i": 10,
   "en": "up. Seems that's what decided it"
  },
  {
   "i": 11,
   "en": "There's light... shining through"
  },
  {
   "i": 12,
   "en": "The net campaign... is it working?"
  },
  {
   "i": 13,
   "en": "If it is..."
  },
  {
   "i": 14,
   "en": "then none of it was wasted"
  },
  {
   "i": 15,
   "en": "Eri, get ready! We're heading over"
  },
  {
   "i": 16,
   "en": "The audition starts very soon"
  },
  {
   "i": 17,
   "en": "Okay"
  },
  {
   "i": 18,
   "en": "Ms. Ozaki... everyone around us..."
  },
  {
   "i": 19,
   "en": "Hm?"
  },
  {
   "i": 20,
   "en": "No one... is looking at me."
  },
  {
   "i": 21,
   "en": "They're all watching someone else..."
  },
  {
   "i": 22,
   "en": "True. Right now, they all assume"
  },
  {
   "i": 23,
   "en": "you're the weakest one here"
  },
  {
   "i": 24,
   "en": "I'm... not even marked?"
  },
  {
   "i": 25,
   "en": "Right. They don't see you as a threat"
  },
  {
   "i": 26,
   "en": "And that's exactly your chance"
  },
  {
   "i": 27,
   "en": "Slip right through the pack"
  },
  {
   "i": 28,
   "en": "and snatch the win away"
  },
  {
   "i": 29,
   "en": "So that makes me..."
  },
  {
   "i": 30,
   "en": "a dark horse?"
  },
  {
   "i": 31,
   "en": "Exactly. When this audition is over,"
  },
  {
   "i": 32,
   "en": "they'll all be staring at you in shock"
  },
  {
   "i": 33,
   "en": "Let's show them all up"
  },
  {
   "i": 34,
   "en": "a pickpocket?"
  },
  {
   "i": 35,
   "en": "Well, in the 'snatching' sense,"
  },
  {
   "i": 36,
   "en": "maybe... but it doesn't sound great"
  },
  {
   "i": 37,
   "en": "...A burglar?"
  },
  {
   "i": 38,
   "en": "That's about as bad."
  },
  {
   "i": 39,
   "en": "C-Call it whatever. Just do your best"
  },
  {
   "i": 40,
   "en": "...Okay"
  },
  {
   "i": 41,
   "en": "a snake?"
  },
  {
   "i": 42,
   "en": "Huh? Why a snake?"
  },
  {
   "i": 43,
   "en": "Well... the slipping through..."
  },
  {
   "i": 44,
   "en": "...Don't free-associate like that"
  },
  {
   "i": 45,
   "en": "Keep picturing weird things and"
  },
  {
   "i": 46,
   "en": "your singing will turn snakey too"
  },
  {
   "i": 47,
   "en": "Okay... I'll be careful"
  },
  {
   "i": 48,
   "en": "Built up little by little on the net,"
  },
  {
   "i": 49,
   "en": "a stage I finally grabbed hold of..."
  },
  {
   "i": 50,
   "en": "I have to make it lead to tomorrow."
  },
  {
   "i": 51,
   "en": "For everyone who helped me, too!"
  }
 ]
}